==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prepollent
<hw>Pre*pol"lent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>praepollens</ets>, p. p. of <ets>praepollere</ets> to surpass in
power; <ets>prae</ets> before + <ets>pollere</ets> to be
powerful.]</ety> <def>Having superior influence or power; prevailing;
predominant.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Boyle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prepollent</ent>⟦br⟧
